account.descriptionLink:
The total supply of FNET on launch shall be 250 million FNET.

10 million have been minted before the mint authority has been transferred to the DAO.

10% are to be allocated for the team = 25 million FNET.
Therefore we need 15 million more for initial team tokens distribution and to enable meaningful proposal voting based on FNET tokens.
account.name: Mint 15M FNET tokens for initial team distribution
